{
  "chapter": 4,
  "chapter_summary": "本章为回忆与现实交织的叙事。宋腾霄回忆当年与孟元超、云紫萝的往事：孟元超深夜来访，揭露自己是金刀吕寿昆的弟子身份，并讲述师父抗清义士的背景及受清廷追捕的经历。二人护送吕寿昆遗孀前往小金川途中，遭遇清廷五名大内高手伏击，恶战通宵，五名高手全数毙命，但孟元超和宋腾霄均身受重伤，孟元超中十三枚毒梅花针入穴道，伤势尤重。丐帮弟子元一冲赶来施救，救活宋腾霄，但对孟元超的伤束手无策。随后宋腾霄回到苏州，发现云紫萝已嫁杨牧并生子，痛苦不已。在小金川期间，吕思美日渐长大，三人关系微妙。云紫萝此时已悄然回到苏州山村旧居。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她为讨么要嫁给杨牧？她为什么要嫁给杨牧？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "text": "你为什么独自跑来看我，却不去陪伴云紫萝呢？现在才不过是二更时分，紫萝想必不会这样早就睡了的。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "speaker_name": "孟元超",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "有一件事情我想和你商量，暂时不想给紫萝知道。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "text": "哦，你也有要瞒着紫萝的事情吗？这是怎么一回事？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "speaker_name": "孟元超",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "这件事情我是要求你帮忙的，金刀上吕寿昆这位老英雄的名字，想必你是一走知道的了！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "text": "你说的是冀北三河县的金刀吕寿昆吗？这位老英雄正是我的世伯呀。我爹生前有两位最要好的朋友，一位是云紫萝的爹爹云重山，另一位就是他了。你瞧这一幅画，这是我的爹爹三十年前的画，画中的三个人就是他们了。当年他们就像我们一样，是时常在一起的。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "speaker_name": "孟元超",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "不错，三十年前，他们是并马三河年少客，这个我也是早已知道的了。不过，后来令尊就没有和这位吕老英雄再往来了，对么？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "text": "你怎么知道？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "speaker_name": "孟元超",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "冀北三河的金刀吕老英雄正是家师。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "text": "哦，你是金刀吕寿昆的弟子。为什么你一直不告诉我？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "speaker_name": "孟元超",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "这是有原因的。这个原因也就正是令尊后来何以不与家师来往的原因！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "text": "我正是要知道这个原因，请你告诉我吧。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "speaker_name": "孟元超",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "说来话长，我先告诉你家师是什么样的人吧。家师表面上是个设馆授徒、不问世事的小邑武师，实际却是个抗清义士。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "text": "不错，我曾听得许多老人说过这个宰相。听说他本来是乾隆的轿夫，因为相貌长得像乾隆一个死去的爱妃，不过几年，便从轿夫做了宰相。做了宰相，只知奉承皇帝，压榨平民，残杀汉人，任用酷吏，贪污枉法，无恶不作。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "text": "令师虽然没有告诉家父，但据我猜想，令师的秘密，家父后来还是知道了的。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "text": "那么你呢，你也是同样的原故逃出来的吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "speaker_name": "孟元超",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "可以说是，也可以说不是。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "text": "这是什么意思？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "speaker_name": "孟元超",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "我只不过是刚刚出道的无名小卒，还没有资格成为清廷缉捕的人物。不过我是奉了家师之命跑到你们这儿来的，要说是避难嘛，也未尝不可。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "text": "多谢你了，孟兄。难得你这样信任我，把什么秘密都告诉了我！",
      "tone": "喜悦",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "text": "云紫萝不会去的！哈，你这句话也未免说得太轻率了，你怎么知道她不会去呢？孟兄，不是我向你夸口，对紫萝的心意，恐怕我会比你明白得多！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "speaker_name": "孟元超",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "我只是猜想而已。我想她们母女相依为命，紫萝未必舍得离开她的母亲。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "speaker_name": "孟元超",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "宋兄是笑我猜得完全不着边际么？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "text": "这也怪不得你，你和紫萝不过相处三年，我和她却是自小一同长大的，对她的为人脾性，当然是比你清楚一些。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "speaker_name": "孟元超",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "懂了，懂了。但我还是不想前去邀她。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "text": "你不好意思跑去求她，我替你去说吧。现在不过三更，紫萝或许尚未就寝。你在这里等，我去去就来。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "speaker_name": "孟元超",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "好吧，你去试试也好。",
      "tone": "冷淡",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zi_luo",
      "speaker_name": "云紫萝",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "你不是元超叫你来的吧？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zi_luo",
      "speaker_name": "云紫萝",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "哦，真的明天就要走了吗？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_yun_zi_luo",
      "text": "你倒底是去呀还是不去？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zi_luo",
      "speaker_name": "云紫萝",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "我很想去，可惜我不能去。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_yun_zi_luo",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zi_luo",
      "speaker_name": "云紫萝",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "不为什么。我爹爹死了，我要陪伴母亲、我舍不得离开她。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_yun_zi_luo",
      "text": "哼，我以为你是巾帼须眉，谁知你果然给孟元超说中，竟是个舍不得离开妈妈的姑娘。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zi_luo",
      "speaker_name": "云紫萝",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "随便你怎样说我，从今之后，你不要再理我好了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "text": "你别哄我欢喜了，我怎么比得上云家姐姐？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "吕思美",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还有谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "吕思美",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他怎么说？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "吕思美",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "孟大哥是老实人，他也跟你胡扯？",
      "tone": "喜悦",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "text": "一点都不骗你，你和云紫罗是各有各的美。倘若你们站在一起，别人一定会把你们当作一对姐妹花。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "吕思美",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "可惜我没有这个福气。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "吕思美",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "你们都很喜欢云姐姐，是么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "text": "不错，但我们也同样的喜欢你。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "吕思美",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "那么云姐姐呢？她是喜欢你多一些，还是喜欢孟大哥多一些？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "text": "我。我不知道。或许是一样吧？",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "吕思美",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "绝不会完全一样的。依我看来，云姐姐一定喜欢你多些，因为你会说话。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "text": "我都不知道呢，你倒知道了？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "吕思美",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "我猜的事儿十有八准，你不知道你就是傻瓜了！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "叔叔，你在想什么，咱们可以走了吧？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_yang_hua",
      "text": "好，现在我就带你去找妈妈。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "真的吗？什么时候我就可以见着妈妈？",
      "tone": "喜悦",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "宋腾霄",
      "listener": "char_yang_hua",
      "text": "不必这样心急，我保管你见得着妈妈就是。今天见不着，至多过一个月就会见着的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 4
    }
  ],
